item.title: You Won't Believe What These Amature Home Makers Have Caught on Video!
item.description: Introduction Every day, amateur home makers are catching some of the most amazing and strange phenomena on video From mysterious creatures to unexplainable natural occurrences, these videos have the potential to change the way we think about the world around us In this blog post, we’ll explore what home makers have been able to capture on video, why these phenomena occur, and how home makers have benefited from this newfound knowledge
